member.summary:
Generates a comparison method similiar to this:

bool Equals(TEnum x, TEnum y)
{
    return x == y;
}

Generates a GetHashCode method similar to this:

int GetHashCode(TEnum obj)
{
    return ((int)obj).GetHashCode();
}

Retrieves via IL the information of the local variable passed in the expression.

var myVar = "string";
var info = Reflect.Variable(() => myVar)

Retrieves via IL the information of the local variable passed in the expression.

var myVar = "string";
var info = Reflect.Variable(() => myVar)

Retrieves via IL the getter method for the property being reflected.

var i2 = new
{
  MyProperty = "Value"
}; 
var info = Reflect.Property(() => i2.Property);
// info will have name of "get_MyProperty"

